  <article class="megamenu__text [ md:mb-70 lg:mb-60 ]">
          <span class="eyebrow [ m-0 ] [ font-america-condensed text-10 leading-15 tracking-wide uppercase no-underline ] [ lg:text-12 lg:leading-22 ] truncate [ block text-red ] [ mt-43 md:mt-0 mb-13 lg:mb-18 ]" >Who We Are</span>
  
              <p class="megamenu__text__content js-ellipsis [ overflow-hidden block ]">Learn about our mission, our charter and principles, and who we are.</p>
    
              <a href="https://www.msf.org/who-we-are" class="cta cta--underline [ inline-flex items-center ] [ font-america-condensed text-black text-10 leading-15 tracking-wide uppercase no-underline ] [ lg:text-12 lg:leading-22 ] [ text-white ] [ mt-20 md:mt-10 lg:mt-22 ]" title="Learn more" id="" aria-label="who we are" >Learn more</a>

          
