  <article class="megamenu__text [ md:mb-70 lg:mb-60 ]">
          <span class="eyebrow [ m-0 ] [ font-america-condensed text-10 leading-15 tracking-wide uppercase no-underline ] [ lg:text-12 lg:leading-22 ] truncate [ block text-red ] [ mt-43 md:mt-0 mb-13 lg:mb-18 ]" >How we work</span>
  
