              <p class="megamenu__text__content js-ellipsis [ overflow-hidden block ]">To upskill and provide training to locally-hired MSF staff in several countries, MSF has created the MSF Academy for Healthcare. </p>
    
              <a href="https://academy.msf.org" class="cta cta--underline no-extlink [ inline-flex items-center ] [ font-america-condensed text-black text-10 leading-15 tracking-wide uppercase no-underline ] [ lg:text-12 lg:leading-22 ] [ text-white ] [ mt-20 md:mt-10 lg:mt-22 ]" title="GO TO SITE" id="" aria-label="msf academy for healthcare"  rel="noopener" target="_blank">GO TO SITE</a>

          
