              <p class="megamenu__text__content js-ellipsis [ overflow-hidden block ]">The MSF Paediatric Days is an event for paediatric field staff, policy makers and academia to exchange ideas, align efforts, inspire and share frontline research to advance urgent paediatric issues of direct concern for the humanitarian field.</p>
    
              <a href="https://paediatrics.msf.org/" class="cta cta--underline no-extlink [ inline-flex items-center ] [ font-america-condensed text-black text-10 leading-15 tracking-wide uppercase no-underline ] [ lg:text-12 lg:leading-22 ] [ text-white ] [ mt-20 md:mt-10 lg:mt-22 ]" title="GO TO SITE" id="" aria-label="msf paediatric days"  rel="noopener" target="_blank">GO TO SITE</a>

          
